646
00:59:49,116 --> 00:59:52,579
[SPEAKER_16]: Tom Lincoln, 27 Gleason Street, Medford.

647
00:59:52,659 --> 00:59:55,661
[SPEAKER_16]: I've been living in Medford for well over 30 years.

648
00:59:56,482 --> 01:00:01,686
